$ HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\MSSQLServer\MSSQLServer

{ LoginMode

? The value of `LoginMode` controls the *authentication mode* for → development/databases/SQL-Server. The following two → Windows/registry/tree-structure/value[values] are possible
  • 1: Windows Only
  • 2: Mixed mode

